271
00:17:27,060 --> 00:17:27,950
He's holding her.

272
00:17:27,950 --> 00:17:31,580
He's got her in this secret underground location.

273
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:34,870
They think that she's gonna talk about my research,

274
00:17:34,870 --> 00:17:38,250
but I keep telling them that she doesn't know anything.

275
00:17:38,250 --> 00:17:40,400
But they won't even admit that they have her.

276
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:45,950
How can you reason with someone when-when they say that
