346
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:07,140
Okay, look, I'll ask 'em, all right?

347
00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:15,230
Mike, you still there?

348
00:22:16,540 --> 00:22:19,490
Yeah.
So when you coming in?

349
00:22:23,370 --> 00:22:27,070
No, I, I got to stop and see someone first.

350
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:30,590
