375
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:20,580
a man who's unable to distinguish fantasy from reality.

376
00:24:20,580 --> 00:24:24,460
But in this situation you've created,
your own well-being 

377
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:30,340
depends on neutralizing him,
on defeating him.

378
00:24:30,340 --> 00:24:33,970
And on some level, that means that you've acknowledged

379
00:24:33,970 --> 00:24:39,050
the danger presented when someone refuses to see things
